@startuml
!include ../../styles/plantuml-theme.puml
title Horizon Bank operating-model traceability (selected onboarding thread)
top to bottom direction
skinparam nodesep 18
skinparam ranksep 22
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam rectangle {
  RoundCorner 8
}

rectangle "CUSTOMER OUTCOME\nUsable banking relationship" as outcome #E8F1FA
rectangle "VALUE STAGE\nIdentity and eligibility confirmed" as value #E8F1FA
rectangle "CAPABILITIES\nCustomer Onboarding\nContributors: Identity Verification;\nFinancial Crime Screening" as capability #EAF4E2
rectangle "PROCESS\nEstablish customer and account" as process #FFF2CC
rectangle "REFERENCE RESPONSIBILITIES\nCandidate BIAN Service Domain responsibilities\nBIAN 14.0 logical reference" as bian #F3E8F7
rectangle "ROLES\nProcess owner; Operations; Control owner" as roles #FCE8E6
rectangle "INFORMATION\nParty; Identity Evidence;\nScreening Result; Account" as info #E5F5F9
rectangle "APPLICATIONS\nCustomer Onboarding Platform; Party and Customer Platform\nFinancial Crime Platform; Core Deposit System" as apps #E8EEF7
rectangle "TECHNOLOGY\nRuntime, integration and operational views" as tech #ECECEC
rectangle "CONTROLS AND MEASURES\nIdentity and screening evidence\nCompletion time; straight-through processing; control failures" as evidence #FFF0E1

outcome -down-> value : is realised through
value -down-> capability : is enabled by
capability -down-> process : is exercised by
process -down-> bian : is informed by
process -down-> roles : assigns work and accountability to
process -down-> info : uses and changes
bian -down-> apps : responsibilities are supported in part by
info -down-> apps : is managed and used by
apps -down-> tech : runs on
process -down-> evidence : is constrained and measured by
tech -down-> evidence : supplies operational evidence to

note bottom
Selected traceability view, not the complete bank.
Mappings may be partial and many-to-many.
A Service Domain is not a capability, process step, team, application or microservice.
end note
@enduml
